Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.82,0:00:10.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以出賣同伴是吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.03,0:00:13.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的  我只是舌頭麻…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.20,0:00:15.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過嘛  我倒是不討厭你這一類的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.54,0:00:24.79,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(696,641.333)}<Sisters>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.54,0:00:24.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轉移處於調整狀態中的妹妹應該是最後一步
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.63,0:00:30.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了防範入侵者以及進行緊急轉手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.21,0:00:32.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該會疏於內部的防衛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.05,0:00:36.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我要那麼做的話  只有趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.48,0:00:52.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,S-Processor  腦神經應用分析所
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.99,0:00:55.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  事出突然非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.91,0:00:58.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能否立即前來敝所
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.08,0:01:02.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍後會為您說明詳細情況的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.69,0:01:31.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與計劃相關的設施可是超過了20處
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.90,0:01:35.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算一個人解決嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.99,0:01:40.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你當我是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.12,0:01:44.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我自己犯下的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.66,0:01:48.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要用自己的雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.46,0:01:50.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做個了斷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.26,0:01:56.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用自己的雙手…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.24,0:04:13.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.28,0:04:16.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以為你被幹掉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.58,0:04:22.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來真是千鈞一髮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.16,0:04:24.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芙蘭達
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.79,0:04:26.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦野
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.96,0:04:28.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得救啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.96,0:04:29.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,服你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.92,0:04:32.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明已經叮囑過你在我們來之前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.01,0:04:35.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要牽制住對方就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:38.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而你卻窮追猛打
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.72,0:04:41.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果還倒蝕把米被人抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.77,0:04:44.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是利欲薰心也好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.35,0:04:45.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不至於會搞成這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.32,0:04:50.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的  芙蘭達
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.53,0:04:53.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我挺看好你這類的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.28,0:04:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「這類」是哪一類的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.34,0:05:12.38,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(797.333,642.667)}<Invader>
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.34,0:05:12.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是  你就是傳聞中的入侵者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.09,0:05:14.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被防住了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.38,0:05:16.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對  是被炸粉碎了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.87,0:05:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,招式還挺實用的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.45,0:05:45.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貼在牆上逃來逃去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.29,0:05:48.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像隻蜘蛛一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.67,0:05:50.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.88,0:05:52.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滝壺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.59,0:06:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.05,0:06:02.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.48,0:06:10.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.56,0:06:11.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒  不在我這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.73,0:06:14.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那女孩到底去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.73,0:06:18.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  偏偏在這最忙的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.99,0:06:22.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要聯繫下那群清道夫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.24,0:06:24.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望別出什麼問題就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.62,0:06:25.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.22,0:06:44.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well  開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.98,0:06:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躲開了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.19,0:07:00.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對  是強制將電擊偏斜了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.04,0:07:09.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎喲  媽耶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.27,0:07:34.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.73,0:07:36.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然還不太明白怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.32,0:07:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那傢伙散發著危險的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.29,0:07:54.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算用障眼法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.33,0:07:57.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種招數連拖延時間都不…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.92,0:08:02.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃跑了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.63,0:08:03.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滝壺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.88,0:08:04.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.09,0:08:05.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.39,0:08:09.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經記錄了目標的AIM擴散力場
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.73,0:08:17.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面對那種對手要以一敵三的話形勢過於不利
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.19,0:08:19.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是優先破壞設施吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.78,0:08:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.20,0:08:25.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能力使用過度了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.37,0:08:27.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經沒有力…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.54,0:08:32.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.75,0:08:34.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經隨機迂迴移動了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.00,0:08:36.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是怎樣捕捉到我的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.79,0:08:37.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亂打的?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.92,0:08:41.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.34,0:08:43.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.38,0:08:48.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被躲開了  搜索對象並未消失
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.47,0:08:51.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是跳到天花板上去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.06,0:08:54.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像她這樣立體式地竄來竄去真夠麻煩呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.31,0:08:56.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滝壺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.57,0:09:01.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依舊那麼強悍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.24,0:09:04.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是
