Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.86,0:09:09.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學園都市排行第四的超能力者——原子崩壞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.37,0:09:13.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再加上  對方就算逃到地球的另一面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.87,0:09:15.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也能搜索其位置信息的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.79,0:09:18.29,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(733.333,637.333)}<AIM  Stalker>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.79,0:09:18.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滝壺的能力「能力追蹤」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.38,0:09:22.96,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(674.667,641.334)}<LEVEL 5>       <LEVEL 4>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.38,0:09:22.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Item引以為豪的超能力者和大能力者的最強組合
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.51,0:09:25.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能從這對組合手上逃掉的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.72,0:09:28.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掉頭來  一個丟米有（到頭來  一個都沒有）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.80,0:09:30.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以所化啦（可以說話啦）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.40,0:09:40.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不知道她是何方神聖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.77,0:09:43.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過要逮住她也只是時間問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.24,0:09:46.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.28,0:09:48.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,步步逼近讓她無處可逃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.88,0:10:01.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御坂美琴的設施襲擊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.88,0:10:07.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算她完成了襲擊  計劃也不會就此終止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.13,0:10:13.68,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(525.333,641.333)}<LEVEL 6>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.13,0:10:13.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名為絕對能力的黑暗  遠超出想像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.65,0:10:24.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將迄今為止收集到的人類情感數據
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.61,0:10:28.20,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(531,642)}<Install>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.61,0:10:28.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,輸入到她們的腦中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.61,0:10:33.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然無法認為靠這種程度的程序能夠萌生真實情感
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.24,0:10:36.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過至少能夠獲得模擬式的反應吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.87,0:10:42.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不知道能否逼停計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.09,0:10:50.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過應該能為她們指示出除了絕望赴死以外的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.43,0:10:56.97,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(753.333,642.667)}<Sisters>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.43,0:10:56.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許從視死如歸的妹妹當中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.72,0:11:00.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出現了對其命運發出哀歎的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.85,0:11:05.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許能有研究者從那姿態中感覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.52,0:11:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是一種超越實驗動物的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.78,0:11:12.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及  奇跡般地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.70,0:11:17.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她們不願再戰鬥的心聲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.79,0:11:21.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,動搖了某人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.46,0:11:28.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然很荒唐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.92,0:11:32.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣做也可能毫無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.14,0:11:34.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.30,0:11:38.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時我感受到的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.15,0:11:49.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考慮到你可能是相關人員所以向上層確認了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.90,0:11:49.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.90,0:11:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在數據類轉移完成之前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.57,0:11:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是超禁止入內的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.66,0:12:01.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然推測出襲擊者是單人作案
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.12,0:12:06.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不能忽視超聲東擊西的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.96,0:12:11.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,防衛組已經收到另一邊設施遭到襲擊的報告
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.09,0:12:12.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並交由游擊隊處理了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.72,0:12:14.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要超堅守陣地便好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.35,0:12:20.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.52,0:12:23.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎麦野的預測超準啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:31.14,banner,,0,0,0,,{\pos(558.667,253.333)\bord0\fs50\c&HD8D2F9&}\N#\N9  \N能\N力\N追\N蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:31.14,banner,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\c&HD8D2F9&\pos(510.667,378.666)}A\NI\NM\N S\Nt\Na\Nl\Nk\Ne\Nr
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.20,0:12:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.74,0:12:41.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芙蘭達
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.50,0:12:42.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.95,0:12:46.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到頭來  預先在設施中佈置好炸彈真是對極了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.39,0:13:04.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然…我的動作已經全被看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.39,0:13:06.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,錯不了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.73,0:13:09.23,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(620.001,645.334)}<Psychometry>              <Clairvoyance>
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.73,0:13:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讀心能力嗎  或者是透視能力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.86,0:13:15.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之  對方有能特定我位置的能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.28,0:13:21.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  這就是所謂的一面倒麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.24,0:13:22.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.58,0:13:31.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請不要抵抗了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.42,0:13:37.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣將你交給委託方  抵抗也是超徒勞的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.43,0:13:44.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抵抗是徒勞?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.14,0:13:49.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Maybe  或許確實如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.65,0:13:52.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,問題不僅僅是這個計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.49,0:14:00.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假設就算計劃遭遇挫折後
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.33,0:14:05.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克隆體能作為普通的人類生活下去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.41,0:14:08.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遭受無情的目光
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.50,0:14:09.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,短暫的壽命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.63,0:14:13.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等待著她們的只是更加殘酷的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.51,0:14:18.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那還不如乾脆就這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.93,0:14:21.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.89,0:14:31.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己也仍然將一切背負起來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.98,0:14:35.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個傻孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.15,0:14:41.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯…這原本應該是由我們來背負的罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.37,0:14:45.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要給予她們開拓命運的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.58,0:14:49.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.42,0:14:51.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.21,0:14:51.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.63,0:14:54.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安裝已經完成
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.25,0:15:00.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她們由名為御坂網絡的腦波鏈連接在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.39,0:15:07.81,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(828,644)}<Sisters>
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.39,0:15:07.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被安裝的情感程序會在所有的妹妹間共享
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.14,0:15:11.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經無人能阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.90,0:15:20.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.28,0:15:22.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不太懂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.45,0:15:26.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過看來你的計劃超告破了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.62,0:15:27.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.58,0:15:30.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼時候有了這種防衛系統…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.89,0:15:45.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何處置她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.55,0:15:48.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把她超帶到上面去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.52,0:15:49.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.64,0:15:50.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.23,0:15:53.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.78,0:16:07.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帳…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.08,0:16:07.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.62,0:16:12.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的話  我也不想用這玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.75,0:16:14.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在  還請你們離開
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.46,0:16:17.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我超不聽話的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.36,0:16:42.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到這時候還避開要害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.49,0:16:44.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然超敬佩你這份照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.45,0:16:49.62,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(865.333,642.667)}<Offense Armor>
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.45,0:16:49.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過區區手槍是無法穿透我的氮氣裝甲的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.71,0:17:00.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超趕快帶她去上面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.50,0:17:01.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.88,0:17:03.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.93,0:17:09.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊的密封艙裡好像有人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.18,0:17:12.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超盯著與工作無關的東西看的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.43,0:17:14.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會因為被滅口而超消失掉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.69,0:17:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.44,0:17:19.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了  快做事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.86,0:17:22.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙會怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.82,0:17:23.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.82,0:17:26.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們只是超按工作行事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.95,0:17:30.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有利用價值的話  應該會留她一條命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.58,0:17:39.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過除了性命以外就只剩一無所有的混帳人生在等著她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.06,0:17:55.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目標向西北方向移動了20米
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.56,0:17:58.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還真難命中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.15,0:18:02.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不單單是立體移動
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.90,0:18:05.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有可能還事先察覺到了我的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.49,0:18:08.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能有這本事的能力者的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.82,0:18:09.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.87,0:18:12.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.20,0:18:18.87,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(625.333,641.333)}<AIM  Stalker>
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.20,0:18:18.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滝壺的能力追蹤雖然便利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.58,0:18:23.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但實則是使能力有意識地失控  不合理地發動力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.75,0:18:26.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能過分使用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.42,0:18:29.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,入侵者也越走越慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.84,0:18:33.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來差不多到極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.18,0:18:36.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繼續使用滝壺的能力的話就不划算了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.60,0:18:40.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被逼趕到這份上也不逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.56,0:18:45.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來是有拼了命也必須要破壞這裡的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.19,0:18:48.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼只要到目的地等著她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.65,0:18:51.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她必定會出現
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.66,0:18:57.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對方是精疲力竭失去冷靜的負傷野獸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.58,0:18:59.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然有危險  但冷靜地對應的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.87,0:19:03.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便不用擔心會輸給她  不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.75,0:19:09.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玩埋伏戰還真是不我的性格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.67,0:19:10.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芙蘭達
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.31,0:19:23.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別停…御坂美琴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.61,0:19:27.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在…沒時間…休息
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.11,0:19:31.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真煩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.66,0:19:36.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招看招
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.80,0:19:53.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜  蜘蛛女
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.43,0:19:55.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.35,0:19:55.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躲不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.19,0:20:06.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果不其然
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.65,0:20:10.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偏斜了我的電擊之後我就預料過了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.49,0:20:14.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙的能力的根本
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.86,0:20:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我的能力是同一種類
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.99,0:20:18.74,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(633.333,645.333)}<Melt Downer>
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.99,0:20:18.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我的原子崩壞偏斜了?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.62,0:20:24.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎  麦野
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.67,0:20:33.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎…原來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.51,0:20:35.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  滝壺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.14,0:20:41.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…沒…事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.89,0:20:44.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…沒…事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.44,0:20:45.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芙蘭達
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.48,0:20:47.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帶上滝壺與絹旗匯合
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.94,0:20:50.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我還能戰鬥…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.98,0:20:52.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不僅僅是考慮到滝壺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.36,0:20:56.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芙蘭達也遭到那個蜘蛛女重創了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.28,0:20:59.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然你在硬撐  不過動作還是太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.74,0:21:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萬一滝壺到了極限  便無法探知敵人何時反擊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.87,0:21:10.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,憑我一人要守住你們倆的話  確實很難
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.50,0:21:14.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  拖後腿了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.14,0:21:20.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並不是在責怪你
